org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.parsing.as

Class MetadataTokenizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.parsing.as.MetadataTokenizer

  • public class MetadataTokenizer
extends Object
    Tokenizes sequences of metadata attributes (e.g. [Event(name="click")]) in ActionScript. Uses RawMetadataTokenizer to get raw tokens. Does not attempt to identify keywords.
